sections.body:
You have the right to:

- request a copy of the personal information we hold about you;
- request that we correct any inaccuracies in that information;
- request that we delete information we are not legally required to retain;
- opt out of any non-essential communications (we do not engage in marketing email of any kind, but you may also unsubscribe from any communications you receive);
- file a complaint with your state's regulator or the SEC if you believe we have mishandled your information.

To exercise any of these rights, contact us at the email address below.
